StoryWeaver (жирный)
StoryWeaver | Branching NPC dialogue
Branching NPC dialogue with conditions, items and quest flags.

Author: Loightik
Compatibility: Paper/Spigot 1.16, 1.17, 1.18, 1.19, 1.20, 1.21, 26.2
Tags: npc, dialogue, quest, story, rpg

About (жирный)
StoryWeaver is a small story engine: YAML dialogue trees, conditions (perm, item, flag, chance), reply GUIs, quest flags and a small API.

RP needs more than one-line NPC replies.

Features (жирный)
• Dialogue trees in YAML
• Simple conditions (perm, item, flag, chance)
• Clickable reply GUI
• Quest flags + a small API
• Per-player progress

Commands (жирный)
Usage: /storyweaver [admin|reload|help]
/storyweaver - dialogue / flags menu
/storyweaver admin - admin tools and diagnostics
/storyweaver reload - reload config.yml and messages.yml without a restart
/storyweaver help - short help

Permissions (жирный)
storyweaver.use - basic commands - default: true
storyweaver.admin - admin commands - default: op
storyweaver.reload - allows reload - default: op

Configuration (жирный)
1. Drop the JAR into /plugins and restart
2. Edit config.yml and messages.yml
3. /storyweaver reload

Support (жирный)
Send server version, plugin version, full stack trace. Discussion or GitHub Issues. Author: Loightik.

